<H3> <TI>   Duma Again Fails To Adopt Budget </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Duma Again Fails To Adopt Budget </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2206104694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1007 
GMT 22 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2206104694 </F>
