<H3> <TI>   Grachev Briefs Shevardnadze on Parliament Meeting </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Grachev Briefs Shevardnadze on Parliament Meeting </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2106161394 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1400 GMT 21 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2106161394 </F>
