<F P=100> Georgia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Parliament Ratifies Black Sea Cooperation Convention </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Parliament Ratifies Black Sea Cooperation Convention </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2206073694 Tbilisi SAKARTVELOS RESPUBLIKA in Georgian 17 
Jun 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> AU2206073694 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi SAKARTVELOS RESPUBLIKA </F>
<F P=105>  Georgian </F>


<TEXT>
