<F P=102>   LD2206100794 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 
0400 GMT 22 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2206100794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Russian Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Vesti" newscast] </F>
  [Text] The staff of the State Customs Committee released 
the first currency control figures relating to the return of 
proceeds from the export of Russian goods. In the last three 
months the total volume of currency retained by exporting 
organizations rather than handed over is $70 million. A total 
of 40 organizations are among the guilty ones. But according to 
observers, the volume of currency which has not been handed over 
in detected cases may seem paltry compared with the amounts of 
currency which simply disappear. One wonders whether the control 
mechanisms introduced are effective. 

</TEXT>

