<F P=102>   LD2206094894 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0937 GMT 22 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2206094894 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS special correspondent Anatoliy Yurkin] </F>
  [Text] Mirny, Arkhangelsk Region, June 22 TASS -- During 
command post exercises conducted under the supervision of the 
Russian defence minister with the participation of President 
Boris Yeltsin, supreme commander-in-chief of the Russian Armed 
