<F P=100> Federal Assembly </F>
<H3> <TI>   Duma Passes Law on External Borrowing </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Duma Passes Law on External Borrowing </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2206211494 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1436 
GMT 22 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2206211494 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Vladimir Taranov] </F>
  [Text] Moscow, 22 Jun (TASS) -- The State Duma today 
adopted a law "On the Russian Federation's external borrowings 
and state credits granted to foreign states by the Russian 
Federation". The law defines the concepts of Russia's state 
external borrowings and state credits granted to foreign states 
by the Russian Federation. It establishes the procedure for the 
adoption of decisions on state external borrowing by the Russian 
Federation and the granting of state credits to foreign states 
by the Russian Federation. The law provides that international 
agreements of the Russian Federation on state external 
borrowings by Russia and the granting of state credits to 
foreign states by Russia are subject to ratification, if the 
amount of the funds being borrowed or granted under the 
agreement exceeds 100 million dollars. 

</TEXT>

