<H3> <TI>   Russian Envoy Links Karabakh Recognition With Armenian Move </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Envoy Links Karabakh Recognition With Armenian Move </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2206142194 Yerevan ARAGIL ELECTRONIC NEWS BULLETIN in 
English 1127 GMT 22 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2206142194 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan ARAGIL ELECTRONIC NEWS BULLETIN </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
