  [Text] Yerevan ("YERKIR" daily--HAYLUR), 06/22/94--Russian 
Ambassador to Armenia Vladimir Stupishin said, status of the RMK 
[Republic of Mountainous Karabakh] is to be defined within the 
framework of international negotiations and should be 
advantageous for the Artsakh people, giving them real security 
guarantees. 
