<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Vladimir Solntsev] </F>
  [Text] Moscow June 23 TASS -- A delegation from the Russian 
Liberal Democratic Party led by Vladimir Zhirinovskiy is going 
to visit North Korea at the beginning of October at the 
invitation of North Korean President Kim Il-song, ITAR-TASS 
learned from sources close to the LDP leadership. 
  The visit will promote the development of contacts which 
