BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS diplomatic correspondent Boris Krivoshey] </F>
  [Text] Moscow June 23 TASS -- The despatch of a 
multi-national force under French command does not fully conform 
to the "classic" criterion of U.N. peacemaking, but under the 
conditions of continued tragedy there it is a necessary step for 
stabilizing the humanitarian situation in that country, Grigoriy 
