<H3> <TI>   27 Constituencies Formed for Presidential Election </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    27 Constituencies Formed for Presidential Election </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2306201294 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 
1600 GMT 23 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2306201294 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Twenty-seven election districts and 33,653 polling 
stations have been formed in Ukraine for the presidential 
election. The electorate register contains almost 38 million 
people. Seven candidates are running for office, said the 
chairman of the Central Electoral Commission, Ivan Yemets, at a 
news conference on 23 June. 

</TEXT>

