<F P=100> UKRAINE </F>
<F P=101> International Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   U.S. Embassy To Launch Economic Cooperation Programs </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    U.S. Embassy To Launch Economic Cooperation Programs </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS2306085194 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in 
Ukrainian 0800 GMT 23 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS2306085194 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Commercial Department of the U.S. Embassy in 
Ukraine has developed four new programs, which, according to 
U.S. experts, will contribute to the establishment of 
cooperation between Ukraine and the United States. The programs 
concern the training of Ukrainian managers directly at U.S. 
companies, a search for partners for cooperation in Ukraine, and 
the establishment of joint ventures. 

</TEXT>

