<H3> <TI>   President Karimov Reportedly Has Kidney Removed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    President Karimov Reportedly Has Kidney Removed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MK2306113594 Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA in Russian 23 Jun 94 
p 3 </F>

<F P=103> MK2306113594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


